    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an impeccable E46 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance. The S54B32 powerplant remains in factory-spec health, featuring a high-pressure VANOS system and six individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response. This example features a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. Mechanically sorted with documented rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement, this chassis is structurally flawless. The suspension geometry is precise, and the exterior finish shows no signs of thermal cycling or environmental degradation. A true turn-key investment for the purist.",
