      "description": "Hey there! I am absolutely in love with this car, but it's time for it to find a new home. It is in truly stunning condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've taken such good care of it, keeping it spotless and strictly following every maintenance check. It drives like a dream and is ready for someone else to enjoy its perfection. You really have to see it in person to appreciate how beautiful it is. Feel free to reach out if you want to come take a look!",
